<h1 id="adjustment-of-the-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate" sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="28">Adjustment of the asset retirement obligation estimate</h1>


<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">For Japan, the initial estimate of the asset retirement obligations (ARO) can be adjusted.</p>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">Use this procedure to learn how to adjust the ARO amount.</p>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">To complete this procedure, the Fixed Assets configuration key must be selected.</p>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">This task was created using the demo data company JPMF.</p>
<h2 id="adjust-the-aro-estimate" sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Adjust the ARO estimate</h2>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Go to Fixed assets &gt; Asset retirement obligations &gt; Fixed assets.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49">In the list, find and select the desired record.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">On the Action Pane, click Fixed asset.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">Click Asset retirement obligation.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">Click Upward to open the drop dialog.
<ul sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">You can also click Downward for minus adjustment.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">In the Transaction date field, enter the date on which to post the adjustment amount.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">In the Upward field, enter the amount of adjustment.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="56">Click OK.</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="post-the-adjustment" sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Post the adjustment</h2>
<ol sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">Go to Fixed assets &gt; Asset retirement obligations &gt; Fixed assets journal.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">Click New.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">In the Name field, type a value.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">Click Save.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Click Lines.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64">Click Proposals.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65">Click Capitalized asset retirement obligation.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">In the To date field, enter a date.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">Click Filter.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68">In the Criteria field, type a value.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">Click OK.</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">Click OK.
<ul sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71">Confirm the adjustment is proposed. The amount proposed is discounted to the present value.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="72">Click Post.</li>
</ol>
